{"tid":1493220,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"85-95 扮工吹水群 「五大訴求，決一不可」","createTime":"2019-08-21T07:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T00:34:40.000Z","uid":207425,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"503b6d3c64f7e0cd6427581bab99f1397a25acc1","tid":1493220,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"Whatapps 扮工吹水群重開啦<br />\n放生左個群半年 <br />\n群主們決定重新招人<br />\n<br />\n招人訴求如下<br />\n1. 85-95 年間既大好青年 <br />\n歡迎各無論讀緊書做緊野或者廢青都好既你加入 <br />\n<br />\n2. 中意吹水識人<br />\n希望大家係群到搵到志同道合既朋友一齊去玩<br />\n<br />\n3. 介紹吃喝玩樂<br />\n香港人生活壓力真係好大<br />\n<br />\n4. 不狗公不狗女<br />\n群主都知大家可能都想出pool, 但希望大家唔會以「搵食」為前提<br />\n<br />\n5. 不割席 不分化 和理非<br />\n明白大家對事有唔同睇法，群主好支持和平理性地討論<br />\n<br />\n入群睇緣份，岩就填表啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdCNbQcodP4vDLTe6BaAE5tBhbSWeUUDqYOKlC_55R5gQNmTw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdCNbQcodP4vDLTe6BaAE5tBhbSWeUUDqYOKlC_55R5gQNmTw%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9okoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=7e21f84f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdCNbQcodP4vDLTe6BaAE5tBhbSWeUUDqYOKlC_55R5gQNmTw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a>"},{"pid":"1509b9fc0287a5f5cf91e0217e700925363b1971","tid":1493220,"uid":207425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n原來標題打錯字"},{"pid":"5a02fab534898d33f707c2aa92ee0b4c93900ae5","tid":1493220,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"040f156720b740bbc14f2efc8d0d287fb30719f9","tid":1493220,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2716f3b2ff027b089b98e5b5e31a4da1622d83a","tid":1493220,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"888